Akro build is a C++ build system with automated dependency tracking.

Akro build is inspired by Maxim Trokhimtchouk's autobuild
https://github.com/petver29/autobuild

Although it borrows many ideas from autobuild, it is a from-scratch,
clean-room implementation.

An introduction to Akro:

http://drpetric.blogspot.com/2016/09/akro-build-extreme-c-build-system.html
